{"tid":787916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩度「又搣又摸」男同學乳頭     正生書院男生被判戒毒所","createTime":"2018-08-21T05:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T07:01:52.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"008ecc883f60b221101329ed6f555b322ab3acc5","tid":787916,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"大嶼山基督教正生書院前年發生男男非禮案，16歲男生趁男同學沐浴完穿衣之際，兩度「又搣又摸」對方乳頭。現年已18歲的男生早前被裁定非禮罪成，今被判入戒毒所接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，前年3月24日下午，事主洗澡期間不慎將衣服弄濕，故赤裸上身、只穿內褲離開浴室，此時被告突然出現，雙手對事主乳頭「又搣又摸」，事主即問被告「你做乜嘢」，又警告會報警，並將被告雙手撥開但不果。事主作供時直指被告當時「表情好猥瑣」，使他不安。<br />\n<br />\n被告於審訊時辯稱只因貪玩兩度「逗」事主乳頭，裁判官則認為被告罔顧事主意願，一而再、再而三侵犯對方，行為猥褻，裁定他罪名成立。"},{"pid":"0666ddaa5c3ff3de9f63e6a93416f838396c6fab","tid":787916,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"hehe"},{"pid":"7670744a0fea43486bcfdfff87c6e3141d075200","tid":787916,"uid":132769,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"粒lin有毒？"},{"pid":"0950d23e75e6ce8da4330ec44d5c413884df4f4e","tid":787916,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"死GAY佬"},{"pid":"32b6d0df0c622b1d1b9f1efcab9d5d6b0c699072","tid":787916,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"戒毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a099d4967861ca86f42ac8c8f4fe6a2ea3ca41c7","tid":787916,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"戒毒所?"},{"pid":"811ec46b5c8ccac78771a2f22d22189a6a248d66","tid":787916,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔連正生書院係咩都唔知？"},{"pid":"fa852b3d698fa65638dfaf87bc45deaa221d879a","tid":787916,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"811ec46b5c8ccac78771a2f22d22189a6a248d66","tid":787916,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score